    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable and stylish ride? This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-maintained, offering a smooth performance you can count on! It\u2019s clean, reliable, and ready for many more miles of adventures. While it has been enjoyed by its previous owner, it remains a high-quality choice for anyone seeking a great value on the road!",
