    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine without a single scratch or chip, while the interior is pristine and completely free of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a smooth, quiet ride with all systems functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle in showroom-quality condition.",
